            </xl>
        </p></section>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h>adjectives</h>
        <section id="adjs-comps">
            <h>complements</h>
            <p><g>trang</g> ≈ <g href="?gd=sgiith">sgìth</g>
            <en>busy and (hence) tired</en> – <xl>
                <li>
                    <gd>Tha Calum sgìth – tha e ag obair gu trang anns an achadh.</gd>
                    <tr>Malcolm is tired – he is working busily in the field.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 7</ref>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <gd>Tha sibh trang ag obair anns an achadh agus tha sibh sgìth.</gd>
                    <tr>You are busy working in the field and you are tired.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 7</ref>
                </li>
            </xl>
        </p></section>
    </section>

